                Iano Patri sacrum <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Titinius Vitalis sevir <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Titinius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> filius <lb n="4"/>Pelagianus Arne<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>sis</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>aedilis quaestor <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>haruspices <lb n="7"/>ex voto posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Aus 9 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt. (B): Saladino, AE 1980: Z. 5: q[u]aestor.</p>
